re he pronounced himself the beast of the area, fell in love with the wrong girl, encounter several challenges amongst others Akpe: The Return of the Beast sheds more light on family values, love, betrayal, life struggle to mention but few. Written by Chris Nzekwe, directed by Toka Mcbaror and produced by Justice Nuagbe; the movie however has a stellar cast that includes Jide Kosoko, Juliet Ibrahim, Bolanle Ninalowo, Daniel Lloyd, Eniola Badmus and Mr. jollof. Why Africans in the diaspora need to invest in Nigeria- Dabiri-Erewa(Opens in a new browser tab) However, the exclusive screening of the forthcoming movie is slated for October 27, 2019 in Lagos and is expected to attract top celebrities and social personalities with performances by Peruzzi and Mr. Real. Vanguard Ace stand-up comedian and on-air-personality, Justice Nuagbe, popularly known as Ushbebe, is fully prepared for the return of his annual comedy show, Chronicles of Ushbebe, scheduled to hold on Sunday, 26th February, 2017, at the convention center of the prestigious Eko Hotel and Suites, Victoria Island, Lagos. February 23, 2017 In "Entertainment" Having distinguished his brand among others, Justice Nuagbe better known as Ushbebe has revealed that preparation is already in top gear towards the 12th edition of his annual event popularly called ‘Chronicles of Ushbebe’ with the 2019 edition tagged ‘Ushbebe Live (Election Edition) Yadadi 12’. February 2, 2019 In "Entertainment" DELECTABLE Ghanaian actress, Juliet Ibrahim will be the host of this year’s edition of comedy and music concert titled, “ The Chronicles of Ushbebe Live,” which holds on Sunday, March 13, at Muson Centre, Lagos. March 4, 2016 In "Showtime People"